    "body": "The idea would be using [slate](https://github.com/tripit/slate) to make the [api](https://github.com/andrewrk/mineflayer/blob/master/doc/api.md) easier to read.\r\n\r\nThe plan is : \r\n* [ ] convert api.md to slate format\r\n* [ ] put the html file in a gh-pages branch of mineflayer\r\n* [ ] have circle ci automatically update the html files\r\n\r\nSome related links : \r\n* [deploying slate](https://github.com/tripit/slate/wiki/Deploying-Slate)\r\n* [slate markdown](https://github.com/tripit/slate/wiki/Markdown-Syntax) (is there any relevant difference to github markdown ?)\r\n",
